# Vercel deploys main.py as a slim FastAPI serverless function via api/index.py.
# All 4 sub-apps (drawing_explainer, analysis_evaluator, chat_drawing,
# news_summary) are included so their /docs endpoints show up. Heavy lazy
# imports (yfinance, pandas, psycopg2, TA-Lib) may 500 at runtime — that's
# expected; module-level boot is what matters for /docs registration.
# Excluded: streamlit app, agent1, MCP scripts, generated content, downloads.

# Generated/downloaded content (largest offenders)
downloads/
video_eng/
video_hindi/
data/
charting_library/
pdf_summaries/
